build: please read ./lib/README

deploy:

  <spring-context class="org.jpos.q2.spring.Spring">
   <attr name="config">path/to/your/application_context.xml</attr>
  </spring-context>

The path is relative to the root of the current JVM

Keep in mind the JARs you will need at runtime vary
greatly depending on the features of Spring in which you
intend to use. Please take a look at the readme.txt file
in the Spring /lib folder for details.
